data.text:
published on 2013-01-04T14:39:28Z

"414 Seconds" is taken from Pere Ubu's brand new album 'Lady From Shanghai' which is due out 7 Jan/8 Jan (US) on Fire Records. Smash the Hegemony of Dance. Stand still. The dancer is puppet to the dance. Order here: http://www.firerecords.com/site/index.php?page=release&releaseid=00000000974 Pere Ubu will be embarking on a UK tour in April, see tour dates here: http://www.ubuprojex.net/calendar.html
